TI  - Comparative Prevalence of Plasmodium falciparum Resistance-Associated
      Genetic Polymorphisms in Parasites Infecting Humans and Mosquitoes in
      Uganda
T2  - Am. J. Trop. Med. Hyg.
JF  - The American journal of tropical medicine and hygiene
VL  - 97
IS  - 5
SP  - 1576-1580
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/10/10
