TI  - Prevalence of Plasmodium falciparum drug resistance markers pfcrt K76T and
      pfaat1 S258L in southern Rwanda, 2010 to 2023
T2  - J. Infect. Dis.
JF  - The journal of infectious diseases
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/2/12
