TI  - Plasmodium falciparum multidrug resistance protein 1 (pfmrp1) gene and its
      association with in vitro drug susceptibility of parasite isolates from
      north-east Myanmar
T2  - J. Antimicrob. Chemother.
JF  - The journal of antimicrobial chemotherapy
VL  - 69
IS  - 8
SP  - 2110-2117
