TI  - Parasitological Clearance Rates and Drug Concentrations of a Fixed Dose
      Combination of Azithromycin-Chloroquine in Asymptomatic Pregnant Women
      with Plasmodium Falciparum Parasitemia: An Open-Label, Non-Comparative
      Study in Sub-Saharan Africa
