TI  - Parasite clearance, cure rate, post-treatment prophylaxis and safety of
      standard 3-day versus an extended 6-day treatment of
      artemether-lumefantrine and a single low-dose primaquine for uncomplicated
      Plasmodium falciparum malaria in Bagamoyo district, Tanzania: a randomized
      controlled trial
T2  - Malar. J.
