TI  - Evolution and Genetic Diversity of the k13 Gene Associated with
      Artemisinin Delayed Parasite Clearance in Plasmodium falciparum
T2  - Antimicrob. Agents Chemother.
JF  - Antimicrobial agents and chemotherapy
VL  - 63
IS  - 8
PY  - 2019
