TI  - Parasite clearance and protection from Plasmodium falciparum infection
      (PCPI): a three-arm, parallel, double-blinded, placebo-controlled,
      randomised trial of presumptive sulfadoxine-pyrimethamine versus
      sulfadoxine-pyrimethamine plus amodiaquine versus artesunate monotherapy
      among asymptomatic children 3-5 years of age in Cameroon
